@Reasoning:
Shared factory for unary elementwise math (sin/cos/exp/log/sqrt/abs/round/
floor/ceil and friends). Each takes one numeric array argument and returns a
double array (elementwise broadcasting). Sharing one factory keeps the
24-plus scalar-math builtins consistent.
@End Reasoning
Process called "create_unary_double_function" that takes nothing returns MatlabFunction:
    Let x_param be make_matlab_param with "x", create_double_type
    Let params be a list containing x_param
    Return make_matlab_signature with params, create_double_type, false, false
End Process

