    Return create_unary_double_function
End Process

Process called "create_exponential_function" that takes nothing returns MatlabFunction:
    Return create_unary_double_function
End Process

@Reasoning:
log(x) / log(x,base) accepts an optional base, returning a double array;
inverse-trig and the other unary forms share create_unary_double_function
but log carries the optional base parameter.
@End Reasoning
Process called "create_logarithm_function" that takes nothing returns MatlabFunction:
    Let x_param be make_matlab_param with "x", create_double_type
    Let params be a list containing x_param
    Return make_matlab_signature with params, create_double_type, false, false
End Process

