End Process

Process called "create_mean_function" that takes nothing returns MatlabFunction:
    Return create_reduction_function
End Process

Process called "create_std_function" that takes nothing returns MatlabFunction:
    Return create_reduction_function
End Process

Process called "create_variance_function" that takes nothing returns MatlabFunction:
    Return create_reduction_function
End Process

